                    </p>
                    
                    <ul class="card-features">
                        <li>Viral trend detection</li>
                        <li>Market demand validation</li>
                        <li>Competitor weakness analysis</li>
                        <li>Geographic opportunity mapping</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <button class="cta-button ecommerce-btn" onclick="selectVertical('ecommerce')">
                        Select E-commerce
